					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Remove the sleep statement.  At 60Hz, the vertical blanking interval is only going to be about 1.4ms long. Your app is not guaranteed to be rescheduled in exactly 1ms, so it's possible that you're sleeping right past the vertical blanking period.</div>

					
